name: Thermaltake CA-1D4-00S1NN-00 Versa H15 mATX Case
description: Thermaltake new Versa H15 micro case is ideal for home-computer builders and gamers, creating enough space for high-end hardware and expansion. The ample ventilation options, cleanable air filter, and a perforated mesh bezel help to keep the entire system cool and dust-free. Versa H15 combines a manageable frame size with extensive options to customize user s computer or gaming system.

name: Western Digital WD10EZEX 1TB Blue 7200RPM SATA 6.0Gb/s 3.5inch Hard Drive
description: Western Digital 1TB WD10EZEX Caviar Blue 3.5 inch 7200rpm internal hard drive. With this drive you get the capacity and the performance you demand to build a high speed, high capacity modern desktop computer. The WD Blue 1tb gives your system the storage it needs and the speed you want - with 1 terabyte of capacity to store all your files, videos, and pictures. Features 64MB cache and a 3.5 inch form factor. This 1 TB SATA HDD has the room you need to store gigabytes upon gigabytes of high definition media, and the read and write speeds to easily access and manage it all.

name: Cooler Master RR-212E-20PK-R2 Hyper 212 EVO Processor Cooler
description: The Coolermaster Hyper 212 Evo RR-212E-20PK-R2 82.9 CFM sleeve bearing cpu fan is one of the best processor fans ever made for Intel & AMD chips - especially with people interested in overclocking. This is a 5-star review type fan from Cooler Master. With the CM 212 Evo you get the most popular cooling product ever released and for good reason - this really is a beast of cooling performance. With a 120mm PWM fan optimized to provide the best cpu cooling experience and heat controlling potential for all the latest processors out there, this fan is guaranteed to reduce your temps over a stock fan even at idle. The fan is mounted onto a highly conductive aluminum heatsink measuring 116 x 51 x 159 mm. Featuring four patented CDC heat pipes that are tightly packed into a flat array on the base. This acts as a virtual vapor chamber that dissipates an enormous amount of heat. The aluminum fin construction has been optimized to give the perfect performance stability between high and low speed fan operations. This cooler will blow any stock cooler out of the park and at this price point it's an unbeatable value.

name: Asus Drw-24b1st/blk/b/as Dvd/cd Writer Sata Drive
description: The Asus drw-24b1st is a high performing DVDRW / CD drive that is capable of reading and writing data on almost all disc formats. The Asus 24b1st is a SATA drive that is black in color and great for managing and creating all your optical media.The ASUS DRW-24B1ST is capable of reading and writing data on DVDaR/aRW, DVDRAM formats. It is a power saving drive and allows you to permanently delete the data on rewritable discs. This provides you with flexibility and efficiency in terms of multimedia data storage and sharing.
